{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b4338d3b88","title":"关于同意国家不为个人祝寿的建议的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"909bf0bcc8","index":0,"year":1955,"month":1,"day":12,"articleId":"b4338d3b88"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji34","name":"毛泽东全集第34卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/34-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji34":{"comments":[{"id":"c33c1f35ac","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"b4338d3b88","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个批语写在全国人大常委会副委员长彭真1955年1月3日给毛泽东、刘少奇、周思来、陈云、邓小平的信上。信中说：黄炎培副委员长曾给全国人大常委会办公厅写信，提议国家不为个人祝寿。我觉得，借黄的提议，把国家做寿的例停止了为好，免得成了惯例，国家要一个接一个地为多人祝寿。如果中央决定接受黄的提议，废除已开之先例，我即把黄炎培的信在常委适当范围内传阅，并在和几个民主人士碰头时，用征求意见的方式作适当配酿，非正式地和党外人士商得一致意见。"}],"contents":[{"id":"be523946d4","type":"title","text":"关于同意国家不为个人祝寿的建议的批语！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"b4338d3b88"},{"id":"c33c1f35ac","type":"paragraph","text":"退彭真。同意这样处理。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"b4338d3b88"},{"id":"9dd82c0c81","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"b4338d3b88"},{"id":"2e600487eb","type":"paragraph","text":"一月十二日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"b4338d3b88"}],"page":{"id":"996e300e6f","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"b4338d3b88","start":419,"end":419}}}},"__N_SSG":true}